half-G
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a flagon, usually of beer, and orig. of half-gallon capacity; b) its contents;

=flagon, =jar, =peter, =half-gallon jar.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
